      <slide>
        <title>Activity 4.2.5 (~5 min)</title>
        <p original-id="MX2-s3a13s1p1" internal-id="p-MX2-c-m-a-a">
  Find the inverse <m original-id="MX2-s3a13s1p1m1" internal-id="m-MX2-c-m-a-a-a">A^{-1}</m> of the matrix
  <m original-id="MX2-s3a13s1p1m2" internal-id="m-MX2-c-m-a-a-b">A=\left[\begin{array}{cc} 1 &amp; 3 \\ 0 &amp; -2 \end{array}\right]</m>
  by row-reducing <m original-id="MX2-s3a13s1p1m3" internal-id="m-MX2-c-m-a-a-c">[A\,|\,I]</m>.
