        <title>Activity 4.2.6 (~5 min)</title>
        <p original-id="MX2-s3a15s1p1" internal-id="p-MX2-c-o-a-a">
Is the matrix <m original-id="MX2-s3a15s1p1m1" internal-id="m-MX2-c-o-a-a-a">\left[\begin{array}{ccc} 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 1 \\ -1 &amp; -4 &amp; 2 \\ 0 &amp; -5 &amp; 5 \end{array}\right]</m> invertible? Give a reason for your answer.
        </p>
